inging. Based on rigorous research into Franklin's voluminous correspondence, essays, and almanacs, this fresh assessment of a well-known figure unpacks the contradictions and conundrums faith presented in Franklin's life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Feb 2020) 0aStatesmenzUnited StatesvBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Political.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300228144423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300228144.jpg  a978-3-11-063898-1  YUP eBook Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles